message: Let's start fair. I take 90%, you take 10%. We can adjust later if you'd like.
My turn! How about a more equitable split this time? I propose 65% for me and 35% for you.
Let's compromise. I'll take 60%, you take 40%. I'm willing to budge a little from my previous offer, but I need more than 35% to make it worthwhile for me.
